<section class="section tension">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow" data-reveal><span class="tick"></span>02 — The problem</p>
    <h2 class="tension__head" data-reveal>
      The most sensitive data you hold,<br />
      <span class="muted">handed to someone else's cloud.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="lead tension__body" data-reveal>
      Resumes. Employee files. Disciplinary notes. Salaries. Every cloud ATS and
      HR suite keeps them on servers you don't control, behind a login you don't
      own. Cadre takes the opposite bet — and keeps it all on your desk.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

